textAfterTable: 6 morceaux Biographie Né(e) : Belfast, ME Genre : Pop Années d’activité : '00s Boasting a soulful croon and versatile piano skills, Lindsey Ray is a Maine-born singer/songwriter who initially performed under the name Lindsey Bachelder. The musician focused on her vocals at an early age, earning top honors at a Los Angeles singing competition when she was only 13 years old. Two years later, Ray began traveling back and forth to New York City in the hopes of landing a recording contract.
